title: Vidafuel Nutrition Closes Oversubscribed $1.075 Million Financing to Advance its Clinical Nutrition Brand
body: Vidafuel, a company developing next-generation clinical nutrition products for use at-home and in the healthcare setting, announced it has closed an oversubscribed $1.075 million financing.

title: Vidafuel Provides Free Nutritional Support to Dialysis Patients in Response to COVID-19
body: NEW YORK, April 2, 2020 /PRNewswire/ -- In response to the COVID-19 pandemic, Vidafuel Nutrition, maker of dietitian-developed nutrition products, has announced a dialysis patient support program ...
